I did not order from your web site.  I ordered the drone from  your video advertisement featured within Rovio's Angry Birds Friends program. The drone shown represented a clone of the Mavic.

The advertised drone that I purchased for example showed a gimbal mounted camera and motors mounted to the tops of each of the four arms. The drone received has neither .

Your video advertisement significantly misrepresented the product received. I view your actions as deceptive and represent a bait and switch marketing strategy!

Drones similar to the one received are available through Ali Express for nearly a third of what you charged.

Don Baker

Salut,

Mesajul tau nu poate ajunge la informare@ing.ro deoarece aceasta este o adresa automata, ce nu permite monitorizarea e-mail-urilor (non-reply).
Daca ai nevoie de noi, ne poti suna oricand la *2ING sau *2464 (apelabil din orice retea nationala, fixa sau mobila) sau 031.406.24.64 (apelabil din orice retea), unde iti vom raspunde in cel mai scurt timp.

Multumim,
ING Bank.


Hello,

Your message cannot reach the address informare@ing.ro because it is a non-reply e-mail account.
If you need us, you can call us anytime at *2ING or *2464 (from any national network) or 031.406.24.64 (from any network).


Thank you!
ING Bank

This is a follow up of the confirmation e mail I received when my order was placed and
paid for in U.S. currency and a charge from London GBR is stated on my credit card. 
As I stated in my previous e mail, I'm not interested in the U.K. version of the Innokin
Endura T18 II as what was stated in the description is the U.S. version which is what I prefer.


 I have have done my research too late as far as your website is concerned. It's only been
launched over three months and traffic is somewhat minimal. Also, I've noticed you have
removed the Innokin Endura T18 II from you site while other sites have it available. This
raises a lot of red flags.
